{"type":null,"faqId":45171,"title":"为什么手机装一个2G/3G的卡后，4G信号反复闪现并且会断网？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.1in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.25in;margin-left:1.1361111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">在4G信号覆盖区域，4G信号闪现后，又瞬间掉网，再回3G。原因是卡未开通4G业务。手机支持4G功能但卡未开通4G业务时，网络会指示手机切到4G，但会被网络拒绝导致掉网。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">建议没有开通4G业务的用户，将4G功能关闭。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span class=\"s1\">选择状态栏下拉列表，关闭4G。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164068\" style=\"width:2.0520833in;height:3.6291666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2. 进入“设置 &gt; 移动网络 &gt; 网络模式“，设置为非4G的模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164069\" style=\"width:2.4409723in;height:4.3395834in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164070\" style=\"width:2.429861in;height:4.3395834in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164071\" style=\"width:2.4631944in;height:4.1in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164072\" style=\"width:2.4631944in;height:4.1194444in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"672","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409598000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":54,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"G卡,信号,掉网","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}